name: The Chicken Squad
overview: Follows a trio of young chicken siblings—Coop, Sweetie and Little Boo—and theirretired search and rescue dog mentor, Captain Tully. Together, they team up on problem-solving adventures in their backyard to help their animal friends, while modeling what it means to be good community helpers and finding the joy in assisting others.

episodes.name: Chicken Squad to the Rescue
episodes.overview: The squad must learn to work together to rescue a stranded pooch.

episodes.name: A Speedy Exit
episodes.overview: The squad gets a little carried away while upgrading headquarters!

episodes.name: The Natural
